{"tid":1239362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣沙咀道m記驚見全部員工講普通話","createTime":"2019-06-18T06:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T08:36:49.000Z","uid":66390,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc4569bb6eeb4cd6cf8f5fd8c4d8b4638ffd950","tid":1239362,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:49:05.000Z","msg":"呢件事真係好恐怖<br />\n有個年青人用廣東話問：「我想要支飲管」<br />\n個呀姐用普通話答：「沒有 環保」<br />\n<br />\n到底發生咩事<br />\n呢班人又有公屋 又有工返 仲要用普通話應對香港人<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n搞掂反送中<br />\n全部香港人都無得休息<br />\n因為仲有國歌法 每日150 仲有真普選等等<br />\n<br />\n簡單講下150人有幾恐怖<br />\n唔講香港唔同機構爆到有幾癲啦<br />\n醫療 房屋都唔提住啦 大家都諗到<br />\n只係講選票<br />\n每日咁樣換血<br />\n香港就日日都有人心淡移民<br />\n而日日都來150個中國人<br />\n咁樣溫水煮蛙法<br />\n過多幾屆 無論你幾努力呀<br />\n泛民要過半數都難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UStFXqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUStFXqX.png&h=eda2d2f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43640514a5c28a2ab230c7c289dfdf0b59930269","tid":1239362,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec55794066b02d3d88cc2538ed08d76ea97512a6","tid":1239362,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"真係好恐怖嫁溫水煮蛙 屌"},{"pid":"63814d1ccf19087e68c58c5d0bb7a8c605e60145","tid":1239362,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"仲有廿三條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be71a6f32ec7385567bfbd3478ada2cfbaabdf16","tid":1239362,"uid":23221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢"},{"pid":"21729948524c84fe1aa293c7373a5826605f2755","tid":1239362,"uid":90743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"repl